This suggests that the paper could belong to the Computational Geometry (cs.CG) sub-category. Additionally, the paper mentions approximation ratios and canonical functions, which are concepts related to Information Theory (cs.IT) and Game Theory (cs.GT) sub-categories, respectively. Finally, the paper deals with network routing, which is a topic related to Network Science (cs.NE) sub-category.
